node.text:
In a film created by Document Journal, Chalvar Monteiro demonstrates the innate harmony between creative skill and the human body’s physical ability. Wearing #MONCLERCRAIGGREEN, Monteiro moves in the expansive, expressive language of contemporary dance, reminding us that the joy and freedom of extending our arms, of feeling our full wingspan without hesitation, is just on the horizon.

@documentjournal
Featuring @chlvrmntro
Directed by @alexblackstudio
Styling by @melreneestyles
Soundtrack @baltra, ’Make It B.I.G.’ from his forthcoming EP, ‘Ambition’, Out May 2021.

node.title: Document Journal Presents: Optimism in motion for #MONCLERCRAIGGREEN

node.text:
In a film created by Document Journal, one of the emerging stars of the modern footwork movement, Ahmad da Dancer,  jukes and shuffles to the beat in #MONCLER1017ALYX9SM by @MatthewMWilliams. Originating in Chicago in the early ‘90s, the footwork movement has spread from the Windy City to countless urban denizens of Detroit, New Jersey, and Baltimore, among others. In footwork, dancers contort and strain, stomping up to 160 bpm to maintain a congruous and almost spiritual rhythm in a beat that combines the traditions of hip hop with new house music — history in motion.

#MONCLERGENIUS

Created for @documentjournal
Featuring Ahmad @ahmad_2nasty
Directed by Lea Winkler @leabwinkler
Styling by Diana Choi @dianaschoi
Music by RP Boo @rp_boo_official

node.title: Document Journal Presents: Jersey Footwork  in #MONCLER1017ALYX9SM

“To me, going beyond connotes motivation, pushing me to constantly reach for excellence by dreaming bigger, while perpetually pushing my own limits. Being a part of Moncler Beyond empowers me to step outside of my comfort zone as an actress, and discover something new in me” actress @crystal_tianai for #MonclerBeyond.
_
Also known as Zhang Tian’ai, Crystal Zhang is a Chinese actress. She is best known for her breakout role in the 2015 hit web-drama Go Princess Go.

The road is mine. The sky is wide.

A new journey awaits. The power of dualism is realised in @veronicaleoni’s latest collection for #MONCLER1952 Woman. Available in stores and on moncler.com now. 

#MONCLERGENIUS 

@mariacarlaboscono shot by @harleyweir for @veronicaleoni’s #MONCLER1952 collection

node.text:
The power of dualism.

The Italian Dolomites provide the dramatic backdrop for @veronicaleoni’s latest collection for #MONCLER1952. Shot by @harleyweir, Leoni’s longtime muse and friend @mariacarlaboscono explores the extremities of nature, escape and deep self-contemplation. 
 
#MONCLERGENIUS

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Moncler on September 06, 2021 tagging @sergiozambon, and @andwander_official. May be an image of 2 people and people standing.

node.text:
Collaboration is key.

Tokyo landmarks meet Alpine peaks for a surreal landscape that lays the groundwork for a new age of wonder. Juxtaposing cloud-like puffers with eclectic prints, #MONCLER1952 Man is a thing of fantasy.

#MONCLER1952
#MONCLERGENIUS
@SergioZambon  

Photography Norbert Schoerner @dayfornightlab @lalalandartists

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Moncler on September 05, 2021 tagging @sergiozambon. May be an image of footwear and text that says 'T MONCLER'.

node.text:
Scale Up.

Supersize your expectations with your feet on the ground and your head in the clouds. The Nirmal shoe has landed with its suede uppers and flexible rubber soles. Whether you’re cliff basing or freerunning about town - these creps have you covered. 

#MONCLER1952
#MONCLERGENIUS
@SergioZambon   

Photography Norbert Schoerner @dayfornightlab @suicoke_official lalalandartists

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Moncler on September 04, 2021 tagging @sergiozambon. May be an image of 5 people and people standing.

node.text:
Turbo pop.

A saturation of bright hues – including hot pink, lime green and saffron – are arranged in vivid juxtapositions with solid earthy tones for an invigorating new way to reflect the light. 

#MONCLER1952
#MONCLERGENIUS
@SergioZambon  

Photography Norbert Schoerner @dayfornightlab @lalalandartists

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Moncler in Tokyo, Japan with @sergiozambon, and @suicoke_official. May be an image of sandals.

node.text:
Keep up the pace. 

For @SergioZambon, fashion is a conversation. This season the designer chose to collaborate with cult Tokyo footwear brand Suicoke – its chunky soles and techy fastenings make it an icon of modern comfort. 

#MONCLER1952
#MONCLERGENIUS
@SergioZambon   

Photography Norbert Schoerner @dayfornightlab @lalalandartists

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Moncler on September 03, 2021 tagging @sergiozambon. May be an image of 1 person and standing.

node.text:
Future facing.

Championing Moncler’s commitment to a sustainable future, the #MONCLER1952 Man collection employs a number of low-impact materials such as recycled nylon and polyester, for a long-term view on style and comfort. 

#MONCLER1952
#MONCLERGENIUS
@SergioZambon 

Photography Norbert Schoerner @dayfornightlab @lalalandartists

node.text:
Tokyo Sunset.

The spirit of comfort lands in public life for @SergioZambon’s latest #MONCLER1952 Man collection. Slippers, capes and knitted tracksuits are hyper-technified and drenched in pop color for a sharp upgrade on downtime classics.

#MONCLER1952
#MONCLERGENIUS
@SergioZambon  

Photography Norbert Schoerner @dayfornightlab @lalalandartists

node.text:
Electric town. 

For his new Moncler Genius collection, @SergioZambon looked to the city of Tokyo: delving beyond the framework of the hyper-kinetic metropolis and into its soft center, to find a new comfort zone. 

#MONCLER1952
#MONCLERGENIUS
@SergioZambon   

Photography Norbert Schoerner @dayfornightlab @lalalandartists
